{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6fe87699-dc61-4bf8-807b-7e2f2dddc39f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6fe87699-dc61-4bf8-807b-7e2f2dddc39f@7.pkg/1772597655630/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597655847", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6fe87699-dc61-4bf8-807b-7e2f2dddc39f@7.pkg/1772597655630/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597655847"}, "identifier": "6fe87699-dc61-4bf8-807b-7e2f2dddc39f", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查角色与责任；题干指出每一份职业都有一份责任，说明需要匹配职业角色与责任。分析选项可知，交警执法、公务员为人民服务是职业角色赋予的，②③正确；公交司机职业见义勇为、环卫工人拾金不昧不是职业角色赋予的，①④错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>每一份职业，都有一份责任。医生救死扶伤、教师教书育人、人民子弟兵保家卫国…由此推知（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①公交司机见义勇为 ②公务员为人民服务</p>\n\n<p>③交通警察严格执法 ④环卫工人拾金不昧</p>\n", "title": "每一份职业，都有一份责任。医生救死扶伤、教师教书育人、人民子弟兵保家卫国…由此推知（     ）①公交司机见义勇为 ②公务员为人民服务③交通警察严格执法 ④环卫工人拾金不昧", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6fe87699-dc61-4bf8-807b-7e2f2dddc39f@7.pkg/item.json?v=1754665048718", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RE